### 8. **Key Patterns Summary**

| Pattern | Used By | Purpose |
|---------|---------|---------|
| **Custom React Context** | Carousel, Sidebar | Share complex state and imperative APIs across children |
| **Error-throwing useHook** | useCarousel(), useSidebar() | Prevent misuse outside provider, clear error messages |
| **CVA (Class Variance Authority)** | Tabs, Sidebar, Select, Dropdown | Manage multiple className variants systematically |
| **Data Attributes** | All components | CSS state selectors, prop propagation without context |
| **Radix Primitive Wrapping** | Accordion, Popover, Dialog, etc. | Delegate accessibility and behavior to primitives |
| **Controlled/Uncontrolled** | Sidebar | Support both controlled and uncontrolled usage |
| **React.useMemo for Context** | Sidebar | Prevent unnecessary re-renders of consumers |
| **Radix Slot + asChild** | Breadcrumb, Sidebar | Polymorphic component pattern with Comp selection |
| **Portal wrapping** | Popover, Dialog, DropdownMenu, Select | Handle layered UI (modals, dropdowns, tooltips) |
| **Callback memoization** | Carousel, Sidebar | Prevent stale closures in event listeners |

