```typescript
export {
  Stepper,
  StepperItem,
  StepperTrigger,
  StepperTitle,
  StepperDescription,
  StepperSeparator,
  StepperContent,
}
```

Named exports at the bottom, matching carousel.tsx lines 234-241.

